{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"WebSocket.readyState","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Konstruktor</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eigenschaften</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/binaryType\"><code>binaryType</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/bufferedAmount\"><code>bufferedAmount</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/extensions\"><code>extensions</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/protocol\"><code>protocol</code></a></li><li><em><code>readyState</code></em></li><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/url\"><code>url</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Methoden</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close\"><code>close()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/send\"><code>send()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Ereignisse</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/message_event\"><code>message</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/open_event\"><code>open</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Vererbung:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p>Die Eigenschaft <strong><code>WebSocket.readyState</code></strong> gibt den momentanen Status einer <a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket\"><code>WebSocket</code></a> Verbindung zurück. Sie ist nur lesbar.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">var readyState = <em>aWebSocket</em>.readyState;</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"werte","title":"Werte","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Einer der folgenden Werte kann vorhanden sein:</p>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td class=\"header\">Wert</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Status</td>\n   <td class=\"header\">Beschreibung</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>0</code></td>\n   <td><code>CONNECTING</code></td>\n   <td>Der Socket wurde erstellt, jedoch besteht noch keine Verbindung.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>1</code></td>\n   <td><code>OPEN</code></td>\n   <td>Eine Verbindung wurde hergestellt und kann zur Kommunikation genutzt werden.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>2</code></td>\n   <td><code>CLOSING</code></td>\n   <td>Die Verbindung wird beendet.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>3</code></td>\n   <td><code>CLOSED</code></td>\n   <td>Die Verbindung wurde geschlossen oder konnte nicht geöffnet werden.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"spezifikationen","title":"Spezifikationen","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Specification</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comment</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/#dom-websocket-readystate\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"de\">Die Definition von 'WebSocket: readyState' in dieser Spezifikation.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Lebender Standard</span></td>\n   <td>Initial definition</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität","isH3":false,"query":"api.WebSocket.readyState","dataURL":"/de/docs/Web/API/WebSocket/readyState/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Werte","id":"werte"},{"text":"Spezifikationen","id":"spezifikationen"},{"text":"Browser Kompatibilität","id":"browser_kompatibilität"}],"summary":"Die Eigenschaft WebSocket.readyState gibt den momentanen Status einer WebSocket Verbindung zurück. Sie ist nur lesbar.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"WebSocket.readyState","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"WebSocket.readyState","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"WebSocket.readyState","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"WebSocket.readyState","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"WebSocket.readyState","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"de/web/api/websocket/readystate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/de/web/api/websocket/readystate/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259